# Festival Network — public site links

Human-facing pages in `docs/` publish to [festival.cpalss.com](https://festival.cpalss.com/). **GitHub Pages renders `docs/` only.**

## Link rules

| Target | Use |
|--------|-----|
| Another page on this site | **`.html`** relative path |
| Repo file (`assets/`, `AGENTS.md`) | `https://github.com/cPALSs/festival/blob/main/...` |
| Coalition-internal paths | **Plain text only** |

See [ai-asset-conventions.md](../docs/ai-asset-conventions.md) § Public site links.
